room_title: Escape room "Ozark Howler" by 417 Escape Artist in Springfield (MO)
room_description: Deep in the heart of the Ozarks, lives the legend of the Ozark Howler. This mythical creature is said to roam the most remote areas of the Midwest. Described as bear size with shaggy black fur, and having prominent horns. Late at night you just might hear the crying howl of the Ozark Howler. It is up to you and your fellow campers to find your way out of your campsite and escape before the Ozark Howler gets you!
